# VibeCraft — Epic Fantasy Knight Fighter
#
# Generated following humanoid modeling best practices:
#   - 7.5-head heroic proportions
#   - Contrapposto stance with hip/shoulder counter-tilt
#   - S-curve spine for natural, alive posture
#   - Bold separated armor plates with gold accents
#   - Strong silhouette readable from all angles
#   - Asymmetric pose (sword raised right, shield held left)
#
# 599 vertices, 846 triangles
# Dimensions: ~2.0 units tall body, sword tip at Y=3.0
# Convention: Y-up, right-handed coordinate system
#
# Reference guides:
#   - thundercloud-studio.com/topology-for-low-poly-game-characters
#   - tohawork.com/en/zeromodelling (low-poly character from scratch)
#   - tripo3d.ai/blog (how to make humanoid 3D character)
#   - my3dmodels.com (low poly character design tips)
#   - overscore.media (intro to low-poly character modelling)

mtllib fighter.mtl

